Query Maximum XOR
key observation:
For XOR:
1 XOR 0 = 1
0 XOR 1 = 1
To maximize XOR:
Prefer opposite bit.

Example:
Current bit:
1
Need:
0
If opposite bit exists, take it; otherwise, take the same bit.

Code:

int getMaxXor(int num)
{
    Node curr = root;
    int maxXor = 0;
    for(int i=31;i>=0;i--)
    {
        int bit = (num >> i) & 1;
        int opposite = 1 - bit;
        if(curr.child[opposite] != null)
        {
            maxXor |= (1 << i);
            curr = curr.child[opposite];
        }
        else
        {
            curr = curr.child[bit];
        }
    }
    return maxXor;
}